{"tid":1982600,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[好想要吧?] 22歲龜癡全屋逾40隻陸龜 大盾臂龜住700呎花園","createTime":"2020-04-21T09:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T08:50:04.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2f795fe2aa4b8c3591962e7d5eedbb9e86f81b45","tid":1982600,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:53:07.000Z","msg":"「其實龜住的地方真的比我的房間及屋更大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」22歲的Oscar家中飼養大大小小逾21隻陸龜，包括能長至30厘米長的印度星龜、豹紋陸龜、紅腿象龜，及逾60厘米長又名非洲盾臂龜的蘇卡達象龜，甚至有一隻世界第二大陸龜、成體能長達120厘米的亞達伯拉象龜。從約12歲開始飼養第一隻非洲盾臂龜起，Oscar就跟爸爸一起不斷在屋前花園擴建龜舍，現時已經逾700呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。在未來當龜繼續成長，就要再鋪設新草皮，將更多位置撥給龜。「龜都好像家人，最希望是每隻都健康。」Oscar最初開始養陸龜的，當時網上養陸龜的資訊並不多，他就拿着字典上外國網站，學習如何將龜養得健康漂亮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200119/PHOZQTQI6DSZMYGHVQYXWJZX24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200119%2FPHOZQTQI6DSZMYGHVQYXWJZX24%2F&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=93075df8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200119%2FPHOZQTQI6DSZMYGHVQYXWJZX24%2F&h=5a4ef19b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200119/PHOZQTQI6DSZMYGHVQYXWJZX24/</a>"},{"pid":"ab92565e4b8bead0053c904dc55af12d30f33f33","tid":1982600,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"在香港有不少人養非洲盾臂龜，最初細細隻時覺得很可愛，但牠們長大後卻因體型太大而要送養。他認為香港真的不太適合飼養非洲盾臂龜，因為很多人只能在室內飼養，然而牠們須要走在泥地、要每天曬太陽、破壞性高，亦須要讓牠們有大量活動的空間。「如果牠們常在室內走階磚地，長年累月滑着腳般行走，盆骨的位置會下陷，對牠們生長不好、會撐不起自己身體。」Oscar亦有盡量幫助龜友收留棄龜，因此家中亦越來越多的非洲盾臂龜與豹紋陸龜。「陸龜買的時候就要預養牠一世，而不是養至某一個大小就賣掉牠或者轉送給朋友，始終養動物真是對牠一生一世的承諾。」Oscar最近亦開設Facebook專頁「Oytp_tortoise」，希望跟龜友分享更多關於飼養陸龜的正確資訊。"},{"pid":"a76582bbe1e91b6233bac96f1f6982b49f44c43b","tid":1982600,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dbYhXNdMpIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdbYhXNdMpIE&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=709c84df\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dbYhXNdMpIE</a>"},{"pid":"62ac93cefdafea089ded433b3112610750af1667","tid":1982600,"uid":150982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:55:28.000Z","msg":"正常人既屋根本應該就係咁大"},{"pid":"5b20279bcbf54c32d242802f80b2d7c25e3c78d2","tid":1982600,"uid":194326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"養緊4隻龜"},{"pid":"be0045b0c9ffe5e855f967fed3062631d922d3fa","tid":1982600,"uid":706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:59:42.000Z","msg":"有無幫佢地改名同認唔認到佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43411f65d9b38db985dec377f7c3cb3c1a410c4b","tid":1982600,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:07:29.000Z","msg":"車厘龜巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ca666f67bc1e3860a98c5ec43ac35da0b43833","tid":1982600,"uid":25952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:13:42.000Z","msg":"陸龜可以成百歲架啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係一代傳一代咁養？"},{"pid":"178321d92348c60b4dafe6519892a4c91764c794","tid":1982600,"uid":108199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"龜龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe06f50c2f24503b3dd70f0ed8a56b1f9ebcb15","tid":1982600,"uid":201512,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"我識自己去廁所同食野，養我好沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f4868df1052e8d324f30c3a79b936052600b12","tid":1982600,"uid":205516,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"一定收起晒啲1仔先做訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\